Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.19,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.35,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.91,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.05,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:22.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:27.13,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:34.07,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret ballot was unanimous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It is decided that Shinobu Mariko-san will be expelled from the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair! That's too severe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too one-sided!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you listen to Shinobu-san's side of the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't speak to her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will leave the Sorority too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now! Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just now left the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,29. The Assembly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You quit the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I quit. Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They expelled Mariko-san, so I decided to leave, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think I would have decided to leave anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cranberry cheesecake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to try some!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Tomoko who picked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A lucky guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tomoko. Shall we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... thanks... later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Tomoko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko's a little strange, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Two or three lost seagulls... headed west,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...searching for somewhere to spend the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Tomoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I knew I'd be expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me on the phone... It sounded like it was Mona-Lisa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that as of yesterday, I was expelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, I never really gave the Sorority a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I really couldn't have cared less about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The more snobbish they got, the more I disliked the whole idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I know that Nanako really got caught up in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she's put out so much effort, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter! It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All that shouting and crying on the swing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That was nothing? Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've completely forgotten all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I told you, I'd been thinking about quitting anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san... you mean... you quit the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:04:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Oh, for goodness sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Tomoko! How can it be such a big deal with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay! If it's okay with you, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. End of story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have some cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Sorority, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so. Once you've been in the Sorority, you think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally I thought there might be more to it than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But, everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're saying, Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good tea! Darjeeling, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The school decided on a punishment for Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was to be suspended 3 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the school think it's doing, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What good does it do to put her life on hold for three months?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This was because some low-life girl was slandering her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Low life"? Who says so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san was hurt! She could have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're siding with the attempted murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"...could have died"? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. Miss Expelled-by-the-Sorority sure is taking big now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with you bitches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I'm not kidding! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange. You don't usually come to hear me play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. About what, pray tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know Misonoo Nanako left the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard something. A rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Um.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... um.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... this isn't the place or time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Not feeling outspoken today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know... before I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some, now and then. Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening more and more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... you must tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming! That must be Nanako and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi again! We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Tomoko-san, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a rash. I have an allergy. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Algebra and geometry are at the scheduled point in the syllabus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in English class today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...we covered up to here and we're supposed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, Nanako-san. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to school for the next 3 months anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy just to see you everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in studying. It wouldn't stick with me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... Misaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She... she was at school. Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san and I have constantly been rivals since Junior High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise her more than anyone else I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an arrogant, self-centered braggart who has to be first at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's utterly alone and desperately lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But... last night I couldn't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes stared into that awful darkness and I thought of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She... she and I are too much alike!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Those very things I can't forgive myself. I see them all in her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I... how could I have been so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko! Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, Misaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What the matter? What is it, Halloween?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been waiting for me to come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Halloween...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A victim... and an assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which of them suffered the greater pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suspension... expulsion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps in the long run, these things are unimportant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should finish telling you the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... I hope you realize you're invading my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,At the next student assembly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't disturb..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,At the next assembly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll make a motion to abolish the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just ride the club's horses anytime you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for permission, and got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's race! Please. Just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to abolish the Sorority?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't be more serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? You don't give a damn about the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you be meddling in someone else's business?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Meddling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly think it is meddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that the Sorority has become a permanent school tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, the Sorority is... the Sorority is Fukiko-sama herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the final legacy of a corrupt tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be the head of the Sorority,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she and the Sorority are separate things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But her pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her final reserve of dignity and pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I shouldn't have mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't let you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Her self-respect is so vital I would sacrifice my life for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong one, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, I love living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is so precious to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't bear to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the winner, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something strange was in the air that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the white doves had left the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not once that morning did I hear the flapping of wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Surely I was not the only one who noticed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Brother, Dear Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in the afternoon, the student assembly was convened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about... the doves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Doves? What doves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, on the occasion of the school's 90th anniversary,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have called this first assembly of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First, permit me to begin by going over today's agenda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about the doves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:42.85,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,We have issues regarding scholastic grading practices, and the issue of on-campus clubs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why don't we take Mariko-san out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea. She's been stuck inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:51.42,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...which are already planning their activities for the first half of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Fairyland?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we may proceed on to the discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam President!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, B-class freshman Orihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You may proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Madam President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I move that the Sorority be abolished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... Could you repeat that, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I move that the Sorority be abolished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Order! Quiet, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Abolish the Sorority?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. Let's put it to a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I must reject this motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the Sorority is part of Seiran's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A school with a traditional caste system?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A "caste system"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you call it a caste system?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The system assigns a value to each person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That value determines how much their future is worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"We're different from other students!" "We're special and elite!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this idiocy goes on and on each year,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and students fight each other to get in, and many get hurt doing so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We would be better off without the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We must abolish the Sorority now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's wrong that the Sorority is so special!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a sort of caste system!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, listen, Seiran is great because of the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's abolish the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doves!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The doves have returned, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Quiet, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please shut up, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone wanting to speak must get permission from the chair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you will not be allowed to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I move Madam President be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She cannot preside over this discussion without personal bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I move to replace her with someone not associated with the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The Sorority president shouldn't preside over the student body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please resign as student body president!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop kissing up to the Sorority!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace Madam President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace Madam President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A problem like this is not one for discussion solely among ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to consult the school board members, teachers, and the alumni.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't allow your emotions to get out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're certain we can get the necessary two-thirds majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Go right ahead, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you think you can so easily abolish this venerated tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...thus, the stormy assembly came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing was decided, nothing was settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But clearly, that day, something had begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been on my mind a lot, since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the best thing for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.91,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped you out because of what I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have to always be in a rose garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She can be her beautiful and proud self without that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If she persists in clinging to those thorny roses,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...they might someday pull her down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...her and her pride both.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Her exquisite dignity and sense of self,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want her to keep all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...because that's the person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.86,0:24:14.06,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:19.53,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:25.14,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:30.61,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:36.89,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:42.36,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:45.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.09,0:24:47.90,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:50.30,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:55.57,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
